abstracts.cdata!:
The proposed project would comprise: the
            construction, and related supervision, of the
            Hargeisa-Borama Road with a link to Tug Wajale in Northern
            Somalia, feasibility and detailed engineering studies of the
            Dinsor-Bardera-Gelib Road in Southern Somalia, and
            strengthening of the Civil Engineering Department of the
            Ministry of Public Works through provision of technical
            assistance, training and machineshop equipment.
